&lt;li&gt;How to set-up &lt;a href="https://geekyshacklebolt.wordpress.com/2020/08/18/how-to-use-a-custom-pelican-blog-theme/"&gt;custom themes&lt;/a&gt; for Pelican by Shiva Saxena.&lt;/li&gt;
